{"tid":1745053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大伏] 星期日一定一定要一早去投票","createTime":"2019-11-22T04:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:49:14.000Z","uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"93e3c9df594840d6ba97561f5d6b129c4d4f3b64","tid":1745053,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"建制呢一排已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無出黎哭喪</strong></span>話唔知點選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好明顯佢地已經背後做晒野, 心諗WIN 撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>大量建制訊息都叫人十一點前去投票</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估計理由有:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><ins>1&gt; 配票</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n唔好再以為選舉係公平既遊戲, 建制係港共幫助下, <strong><ins>有大把手段去控制選舉結果</ins></strong><br />\n選舉名冊係政府控制, 有幾多人, 邊個人有權投, 無人知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>猜想係有一班人可以重覆投</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而係有人去數每區一早既投票人數去做配票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以必須要攪亂佢地步處<br />\n一早去投<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: green;\">2&gt; 腰斬投票</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n有人話會搵人攪事, 腰斬投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然我覺得可能性不大<br />\n但唔可以用常理去再諗港共做既野<br />\n<strong><ins>而且依家最需要區選既係港共</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為係變相公投<br />\n佢地WIN 左就可以話大眾支持止暴制亂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3&gt; 監票</span></strong></span><br />\n老實講, 今年有狗係門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經唔知能唔能夠順利監票<br />\n大家如果去監票, 切記一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">街坊LOOK</span> 唔好著黑衫<br />\n同埋<span style=\"color: green;\">忍忍忍忍忍忍忍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以俾狗有藉口開波趕你地走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">我已經成功說服兩老投票</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請各位手足放下成見<br />\n今次投票結果絕對係直接影響到運動進程<br />\n<br />\n我地形勢講真係超級不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>盡量將已決定既結局改寫</strong></span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大家要團結<br />\n被捕手足既未來, 掌握係我地手上</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幫推</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44730209b0a70c5b1d21cfa3dd6f12f77810bea","tid":1745053,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:42:08.000Z","msg":"一早去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075f4e1986e8f90cf0e2a15456b9effe4acd49ad","tid":1745053,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"一早去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050d02c5f7289df70ebb7f65af79f6ced2a11234","tid":1745053,"uid":230703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8wZEpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8wZEpd.png&h=440005b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dd04b91a69e90e571dbd7771140540a307813b1","tid":1745053,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"050d02c5f7289df70ebb7f65af79f6ced2a11234","tid":1745053,"uid":230703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8wZEpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8wZEpd.png&h=440005b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"約老豆老母8 點飲茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早一齊投"},{"pid":"30e10c9a243aba58f934982d19d486bceb4d4cfd","tid":1745053,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:49:14.000Z","msg":"一早去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}